'''[[Rangers F.C.]]''' has a long and illustrious history. Formed in 1872, [[Rangers F.C.|Rangers]] are the first, and only, club in the world to have won more than 50 national league titles. The club is also the most honoured in the world having won 113 trophies in total. Despite being formed 137 years ago Rangers have only ever been managed by twelve different men.
